{t:E-0110 (F) GIVE HEED TO MY WORDS O LORD}
{st:}
E-0110
F CHORD

Give heed to my words, O Lord,
Consider my meditation.
Hearken unto the voice of my cry,
My King and my God,
For Lord unto Thee will I pray.
My voice shall Thou hear in the morning.
O Lord in the morning will I direct my
Prayer unto Thee, and will look up !
{genre:Devotion}
